---

## Scan Execution Checklist

| Recipe | Hits |
|--------|------|
| `.Substring()` | 0 |
| `.ToLower()`/`.ToUpper()` | 0 |
| `.Replace()` | 0 |
| `params` | 0 |
| `Regex` | 0 |
